thanks for presenting today. Yeah, I was thinking about athlete performance. And I don't know if

00:40:07.541 --> 00:40:13.142
that's something that you do or work with that kind of data, but it seems to me there's a lot

00:40:13.142 --> 00:40:18.661
of factors that would influence an athlete to perform well or not so well and made me think

00:40:18.661 --> 00:40:25.142
about secondary data sources. Like, is that something you do? And if so, are athletes

00:40:25.142 --> 00:40:30.582
interested in participating in that by, I guess, willingly give up some of their personal health

