00:41:37.461 --> 00:41:43.622
privacy violation. I don't think it would work. I don't think it would go well in our league

00:41:43.622 --> 00:41:51.942
personally. Let me see what else I want to cover there. Yeah, those are kind of the big things.

00:41:52.742 --> 00:42:00.341
