uses it, it's a little bit harder to get that experience, right? But there are ways that you

00:48:08.182 --> 00:48:12.341
can learn. Do you have any tips? Well, first of all, I will say that when I started working with

00:48:12.341 --> 00:48:17.302
Snowflake, I had never used it before, so that was fun, and that's okay. Sometimes you learn

00:48:17.302 --> 00:48:23.381
