00:49:34.021 --> 00:49:39.862
we have players that have majored in computer science or math or are just interested in data,

00:49:39.862 --> 00:49:44.741
so that's been really cool to give them fun high-level intros on what we're doing.

00:49:46.741 --> 00:49:51.062
I'm not worried about them trying to optimize for stats because we use lots of things in our

00:49:51.062 --> 00:49:59.942
decision-making processes, to be honest. That is not my big concern. I'm more concerned about them

00:50:00.901 --> 00:50:05.702
I mean, it's good that data is publicly accessible. I would love them to just use us

